  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK49">
<l>aṟaṉeṉap paṭṭatē yilvāḻkkai yaḵtum</l>
<l>piṟaṉpaḻippa tillāyi ṉaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is domestic life that is called dharma; that [other]</l>
<l>is also good—if another does not despise it!</l>
<l>(Interpretation of Maṇakkuṭavar:</l>
<l>"It is domestic life that is called dharma, and it is good</l>
<l>if it does not have something for another to blame.")</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
